{"tid":1380090,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"728後最新解答疑問 [推到全人類有豬嘴] 百幾蚊就100%防!!!! 豬嘴護目鏡攻略(應對對方升級催淚彈)!!","createTime":"2019-07-29T02:37:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T13:56:23.000Z","uid":105976,"like":90,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"31cee14bbc68dc34f45db3bde29a494d02b0c82d","tid":1380090,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:37:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>3M 自己話 filter 係可以用 40 小時, or 第一次用後 30 日內要掉. 濃度高時, 時間會短啲. </strong></span></span> 多謝無名博士解答   所以其實係因為大家d濾罐用左超過1個月開始老化<br />\n濾罐要換新<br />\nHIS fb link: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Dr.Incognito.HK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FDr.Incognito.HK%2F&d=WXcHt8yLUpgx7cmMWxn67XyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=445ec84c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Dr.Incognito.HK/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">經過兄弟裝修實測<br />\n連$100既3200+3311k 戴得好 近距裝修都絕對防禦</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n728後 發現濃度有所提升 plan1 同 2C plan可能唔夠做 <br />\n千奇唔好濕水 濕水filter會失效<br />\n濃度太高filter時限都會減少 要買定filter換<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">全防具spreadsheet (強烈建議睇 , 最好pc睇) 內有購買連結</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1X_p56W1VLpfWTqdVb3-C8wlLMzfcy8qH6h8w41VTyu4/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1X_p56W1VLpfWTqdVb3-C8wlLMzfcy8qH6h8w41VTyu4%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=WXcHt8yLUpgx7cmMWxn67XyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=e286e53c\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1X_p56W1VLpfWTqdVb3-C8wlLMzfcy8qH6h8w41VTyu4/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n無論和平定勇武 裝修都一定會被放煙<br />\n如果一食煙就退 前面既工友就冇人支援<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">所以保護自已=保護他人 無論果次裝修講到明好安全<br />\n都一定要帶齊安全裝備</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n首先 對付既係有機氣體+大量結晶體 防塵果D口罩/外科口罩係冇用<br />\n所以濾罐能力要 防有機氣體 + P100級既濾棉 (100%防顆粒)<br />\n仲要配密氣式護目鏡 (泳鏡or 氣密式鏡 一定要non-vented!!!)<br />\n泳鏡其實都有好細既孔 搵到就用玻璃膠封住<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">護目鏡推呢隻 火場用 完全氣密</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B07CQFYTCT/ref=ox_sc_act_image_1?smid=ATVPDKIKX0DER&amp;psc=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB07CQFYTCT%2Fref%3Dox_sc_act_image_1%3Fsmid%3DATVPDKIKX0DER%26psc%3D1&d=WXcHt8yLUpgx7cmMWxn67XyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=b576a720\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B07CQFYTCT/ref=ox_sc_act_image_1?smid=ATVPDKIKX0DER&amp;psc=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記住防具係保護自已 唔會犯法, 每個人都有更加唔洗驚俾人針對<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">濾罐時效有40小時 (戴住呼吸先計) (濃度太高會加速老化)<br />\n用完用密實袋包好佢 下次再用 有效期大約1個月</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n懶人包: (以下豬嘴+濾罐濾棉都係3M牌子, 每一隻plan都100%防)<br />\n1. <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">3200豬嘴 + 3311k濾罐</span></strong> (防有機氣體+防晶體) (實測100%防 戴住長期跑會有點呼吸不順)<br />\n一套大約140蚊<br />\n任何一間五金鋪入去問佢 90%都有 <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">2. (A)6200/6500/7500豬嘴+ 60926濾罐</span></strong> (防有機氣體+ 100%防晶體) (難買, 實測100%防)<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">60921 60923 60925 69028 都同樣有效 </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n豬嘴6200 6500 7500 5金鋪都會搵到 真係冇先上網買 因為運過黎都要成星期 (雖然網購平d)<br />\n<br />\n602926購買連結: 1對22usd<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/3M-Cartridge-60926-Respiratory-Protection/dp/B009POHLRC/ref=sr_1_2_sspa?crid=263BB1V1XWE2J&amp;keywords=3m+6006+cartridge&amp;qid=1564048054&amp;s=gateway&amp;sprefix=3M+6006%2Caps%2C835&amp;sr=8-2-spons&amp;psc=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2F3M-Cartridge-60926-Respiratory-Protection%2Fdp%2FB009POHLRC%2Fref%3Dsr_1_2_sspa%3Fcrid%3D263BB1V1XWE2J%26keywords%3D3m%2B6006%2Bcartridge%26qid%3D1564048054%26s%3Dgateway%26sprefix%3D3M%2B6006%252Caps%252C835%26sr%3D8-2-spons%26psc%3D1&d=WXcHt8yLUpgx7cmMWxn67XyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=8a6c9087\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/3M-Cartridge-60926-Respiratory-Protection/dp/B009POHLRC/ref=sr_1_2_sspa?crid=263BB1V1XWE2J&amp;keywords=3m+6006+cartridge&amp;qid=1564048054&amp;s=gateway&amp;sprefix=3M+6006%2Caps%2C835&amp;sr=8-2-spons&amp;psc=1</a><br />\n<br />\n(B) <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">6200/6500/7500豬嘴 + 6006濾罐 + 502 外蓋 + 2091濾棉</span></strong> (100%防晶體) (實測100%防)<br />\n瀘罐6006都係5金鋪買就有 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><br />\n2091 2096 2097 2291 2296 2297 都一樣有效!!!</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n502外蓋購買連結:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Compatible-Respirator-Prefilters-Prefilter-Adaptor/dp/B07Q87NPN3/ref=sr_1_4?keywords=3m+502&amp;qid=1564048174&amp;s=gateway&amp;sr=8-4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FCompatible-Respirator-Prefilters-Prefilter-Adaptor%2Fdp%2FB07Q87NPN3%2Fref%3Dsr_1_4%3Fkeywords%3D3m%2B502%26qid%3D1564048174%26s%3Dgateway%26sr%3D8-4&d=WXcHt8yLUpgx7cmMWxn67XyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=05fc5f4d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/Compatible-Respirator-Prefilters-Prefilter-Adaptor/dp/B07Q87NPN3/ref=sr_1_4?keywords=3m+502&amp;qid=1564048174&amp;s=gateway&amp;sr=8-4</a><br />\n<br />\n2901濾棉 1對7usd<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/3M-Filter-2091P100-2-Bag/dp/B001D1JCK4/ref=sr_1_12?keywords=3m+2901+filter&amp;qid=1564048476&amp;s=gateway&amp;sr=8-12\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2F3M-Filter-2091P100-2-Bag%2Fdp%2FB001D1JCK4%2Fref%3Dsr_1_12%3Fkeywords%3D3m%2B2901%2Bfilter%26qid%3D1564048476%26s%3Dgateway%26sr%3D8-12&d=WXcHt8yLUpgx7cmMWxn67XyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=09dde113\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/3M-Filter-2091P100-2-Bag/dp/B001D1JCK4/ref=sr_1_12?keywords=3m+2901+filter&amp;qid=1564048476&amp;s=gateway&amp;sr=8-12</a><br />\n<br />\n(C) 6200/6500/7500豬嘴 + 2097濾棉 (呢隻濾棉可以防埋有機氣體+顆粒) 2207棉係新版 一樣得 (對家升級左催淚彈, 濃度太高呢個plan可能唔夠做)<br />\n<br />\n3. 全臉式 3M 6000 OR 6800 + 上面既濾罐 大約700~800蚊 慳返唔洗買護目鏡 其實唔係貴好多<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/3M-Respirator-6800-Respiratory-Protection/dp/B007JZ1LG6/ref=sr_1_1?keywords=3M+full+face&amp;qid=1564045122&amp;refinements=p_n_condition-type%3A6461716011&amp;rnid=6461714011&amp;s=gateway&amp;sr=8-1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2F3M-Respirator-6800-Respiratory-Protection%2Fdp%2FB007JZ1LG6%2Fref%3Dsr_1_1%3Fkeywords%3D3M%2Bfull%2Bface%26qid%3D1564045122%26refinements%3Dp_n_condition-type%253A6461716011%26rnid%3D6461714011%26s%3Dgateway%26sr%3D8-1&d=WXcHt8yLUpgx7cmMWxn67XyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=3649af17\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/3M-Respirator-6800-Respiratory-Protection/dp/B007JZ1LG6/ref=sr_1_1?keywords=3M+full+face&amp;qid=1564045122&amp;refinements=p_n_condition-type%3A6461716011&amp;rnid=6461714011&amp;s=gateway&amp;sr=8-1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2097連結:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/3M-Particulate-Filter-Organic-Filters/dp/B079X5C3QP/ref=sr_1_2?keywords=3m+2907&amp;qid=1564048531&amp;s=gateway&amp;sr=8-2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2F3M-Particulate-Filter-Organic-Filters%2Fdp%2FB079X5C3QP%2Fref%3Dsr_1_2%3Fkeywords%3D3m%2B2907%26qid%3D1564048531%26s%3Dgateway%26sr%3D8-2&d=WXcHt8yLUpgx7cmMWxn67XyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=b9746f51\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/3M-Particulate-Filter-Organic-Filters/dp/B079X5C3QP/ref=sr_1_2?keywords=3m+2907&amp;qid=1564048531&amp;s=gateway&amp;sr=8-2</a><br />\n<br />\n60926濾罐難買 AMAZON有, 可以俾多少少錢特快運 都平過HK五金鋪<br />\n要快就記得選特快運送mode<br />\n<br />\n6200/6500/7500 都係雙濾罐設計 用既濾罐都一樣 愈高級愈戴得舒服/愈氣密/愈貴 <br />\n<br />\n上場之前記得測試氣密度<br />\n用手輕按住口罩前方既換氣蓋<br />\n之後用少少力吹氣 如果冇空氣由豬嘴貼住面部既gap位到漏走 你豬嘴就成功氣密左<br />\n<br />\n至於點解琴晚大家覺得豬嘴有d唔夠頂 仲研究緊 有更新會即刻俾大家知 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最新催淚彈成份表<br />\n化學jj請幫手睇<br />\n80%都係cs gas (同其他一樣)<br />\n應該就冇新奇怪成份  <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7EQro1D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7EQro1D.png&h=f37bca20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n博士q&amp;a<br />\n博士解答: Q:<br />\n1. 對家換左唔同成份催淚彈<br />\n2. filter濕左水?<br />\n3. 戴得唔夠緊 漏氣<br />\n4. 係因為濃度太高 所以有效時間會大減????<br />\n5. 口罩正前方咪有塊圓膠片仔 會唔會係打開果陣有污染物飄左入去???? <br />\n<br />\nA:<br />\n1. 其實主要係得兩隻, 但即使轉咗. filter cartridge 會用一樣<br />\n<br />\n2. filter濕左水? P100 濕咗水係唔得<br />\n<br />\n3. 戴得唔夠緊 漏氣<br />\n要做 Fit test, 有人可能買得太大或大細, 講緊面罩, 本身有 size<br />\n做呢個 User seal check (我會做晒 positive 同 negative) 8:15 到 10:35:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yBg2B2BP9nA?t=496\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyBg2B2BP9nA%3Ft%3D496&d=WXcHt8yLUpgx7cmMWxn67XyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=12e0928b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yBg2B2BP9nA?t=496</a><br />\n會漏, 一係唔夠 tight, 拉 tight 啲. 一係就本身買錯 size.<br />\n<br />\n4. 係因為濃度太高 所以有效時間會大減????<br />\n第一, 當濃度太高時, 其實只用 passive respirator 係未必夠. 要好似消防咁有 Air supply. 所以, 就算有啱嘅呼吸裝備, 都唔好响超高濃度煙霧環境逗留. 第二, 假如用 6xxx, 502, 2xxx (p100) 嘅人, 可考慮換新餅 (p100, 2xxx). filter 用得耐, 會 saturated/滿. 物理性嘅玩完先. <br />\n<br />\n5. 口罩正前方咪有塊圓膠片仔 你吹氣佢就會微微打開俾d氣走<br />\n呢個應唔會入到多少. 個設計係你呼氣時先會開, 呼氣會吹開啲嘢, 唔會引入 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3M 自己話 filter 係可以用 40 小時, or 第一次用後 30 日內要掉. 濃度高時, 時間會短啲. <br />\n重有, 要記得, 啲嘢會由皮膚入, 速度唔會好快, 但都會. 濃度高時, 短衫短褲會不知不覺入咗而唔舒服."},{"pid":"83e96f233feae51a2f8211be6afa2d505c5b3700","tid":1380090,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:38:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"370a849f2d68c255f5dd6cf9fffbe1750969a4b6","tid":1380090,"uid":105976,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:39:45.000Z","msg":"另有巴打建議:<br />\nP100濾綿優先買2096/2097/2296/2297<br />\n效用更佳 無先買2091/2291"},{"pid":"8c0e65e4520c737df82aeab367be0d3f0ec78344","tid":1380090,"uid":105976,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:43:17.000Z","msg":"博士:＿<br />\n<br />\n不過買 2296/2297 會好過 2096/ 2097<br />\n<br />\n同埋, 2296 同2096 嘅 Acid Gas 係無用, 因 3M list 了的 acid gas 係 HCl, H2S, SO2, Cl2. 都冇需要"},{"pid":"9883873c63ae296bd87f9c72438155682bfdbca8","tid":1380090,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:44:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d002464e95bce985e39eea63239cff66dc8c1fce","tid":1380090,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:46:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcb213b141cebe963062b31959a36c09027dadc9","tid":1380090,"uid":42007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:47:52.000Z","msg":"巴打覺得集運會唔會俾人賣資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17c109e8e5e24169231184e8de83eac7865009a5","tid":1380090,"uid":41460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:48:26.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"a441acbbec4fca4e2b55581122e16c3d02c663c1","tid":1380090,"uid":267197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:48:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a92b964f3d4ee90e542ae1c5e09575a42172ce69","tid":1380090,"uid":182998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:48:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4349e7fed943bf3ccbabed5b1a7dc77678643bff","tid":1380090,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dcb213